data.description: You will love this charming Washington Local brick ranch with a full basement! Updated and ready for you to move in! Some of the updates include: new ceiling fans, flooring, newer HVAC, tiled shower and jetted tub, new high quality blinds, 10 year old roof, water heater new in 23', new basement carpeting for lots of additional living area! The yard is fully fenced, with great space, a fire pit, and a patio. Don't wait on this one!
